A lot of people
work in the kitchen.

12:02.250 --> 12:03.917
A lot of people
hate Schibetta.

12:03.917 --> 12:05.333
- All right, all right.

12:05.333 --> 12:07.750
Lenny,
keep investigating.

12:07.750 --> 12:10.208
You get any solid evidence
that Adebisi was involved,

12:10.208 --> 12:11.709
we'll deal with him.

12:11.709 --> 12:13.125
- And if not?

12:13.125 --> 12:16.375
- Then this one goes in
the unsolved mysteries file.

12:21.667 --> 12:23.667
[monitors beeping]

12:23.667 --> 12:25.125
- Hey.

12:26.750 --> 12:29.250
- What do you want?

12:29.250 --> 12:32.166
- To tell you that Glynn ain't
doing dick about what happened.

12:32.166 --> 12:34.625
- That's fine,
I'll take care of it myself.

12:34.625 --> 12:35.834
- How?

12:36.875 --> 12:39.167
- Wait and see.

12:39.167 --> 12:40.166
- Peter...

12:45.875 --> 12:48.126
