is embarrassed.

12:49.042 --> 12:50.875
- They got no reason
to be embarrassed.

12:50.875 --> 12:52.750
- They're unhappy
with the way

12:52.750 --> 12:54.625
that you're
running things in here.

12:54.625 --> 12:56.500
- They blame me
for getting poisoned?

12:56.500 --> 13:00.375
- Your father got fed ground
glass over the course of months.

