13:16.084 --> 13:20.458
- This is what they say,
the family.

13:20.458 --> 13:21.917
- Christ.

13:22.834 --> 13:25.125
You tell them that
I'm gonna handle Adebisi.

13:25.125 --> 13:27.333
I'm gonna get
my honor back.

13:27.333 --> 13:29.126
