30th wedding anniversary

36:39.500 --> 36:41.625
in the Virgin Islands.

36:41.625 --> 36:44.500
Talk about
living in the past.

36:44.500 --> 36:46.458
Other than that,
I'm hunki-dory.

36:46.458 --> 36:48.084
You?

36:48.084 --> 36:50.250
- Eh.
