36:58.333 --> 37:00.209
- You want me
to give you marijuana.

37:00.209 --> 37:01.417
- Yeah.

37:01.417 --> 37:04.209
For, what do you call it?
Medicinal purposes.

37:04.209 --> 37:06.209
- Nice try, kid.

37:08.375 --> 37:10.166
