54:23.417 --> 54:30.500
♪ ♪

54:31.917 --> 54:33.375
Motherfuckers!

54:33.375 --> 54:35.166
Motherfuckers!

54:40.375 --> 54:42.084
Ah!

54:42.875 --> 54:45.917
[screaming]

54:53.625 --> 55:00.667
♪ ♪

55:14.167 --> 55:17.250
[muffled alarm buzzing]

55:26.875 --> 55:33.917
♪ ♪

55:49.542 --> 55:52.042
- [panting]

55:56.417 --> 56:00.625
♪ Hannah Bantry in the pantry
gnawing at a mutton bone ♪

56:00.625 --> 56:03.167
♪ How she gnawed it,
how she clawed it ♪

56:03.167 --> 56:06.750
♪ When she found
herself alone ♪

56:08.041 --> 56:15.125
♪ ♪

56:32.291 --> 56:34.750
[coughing]

56:38.542 --> 56:41.750
- At the end of the day,

56:41.750 --> 56:43.500
a bed is
the best friend you got.

56:43.500 --> 56:45.959
Sure, the mattress
may be lumpy,

56:45.959 --> 56:47.709
the springs may have sprung,

56:47.709 --> 56:52.792
the bed itself may be
in some seedy motel or in Oz.

56:52.792 --> 56:55.250
But the bed...

56:56.375 --> 56:58.167
It beckons you.

56:58.167 --> 57:00.834
It comforts, it cradles
until you sleep.

57:00.834 --> 57:02.834
And if you're
lucky enough

57:02.834 --> 57:05.041
to have the right person
lying next to you, shit,

57:05.041 --> 57:06.750
there ain't a reason you got
to get out

57:06.750 --> 57:08.709
of that bed come morning.

57:09.333 --> 57:12.667
Good night.

57:12.667 --> 57:14.209
Sleep tight.

57:14.209 --> 57:16.375
Don't let
the bed bugs bite.

